{"tid":1062769,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"台灣工程師：AMD 對於 VMM、VDI、RDM、IO passthru 還有一段路要走..不要硬來，會出事...","createTime":"2019-03-15T10:04:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-20T06:02:59.000Z","uid":1886,"like":9,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"92ca3982a223b487b6dd4111cb48f5fe8bec0361","tid":1062769,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T10:04:14.000Z","msg":"故事是這樣講開始的&ndash;&ndash;&ndash;AMD 與 Intel 專業用途取捨<br />\n<br />\n某間知名自動化設備公司為了省軟體授權費<br />\n想用VDI(※註1)來實現授權移轉<br />\n順便連硬體一併更新<br />\n<br />\nA承包使用了9900K 驗證可用性，且壓力測試通過<br />\n(Solidwork、solid edge、CATIA、Pro/E、ACAD、inventor，還有 vmware horizon 顯卡VDI，Storage VASA、VAAI等功能)<br />\n<br />\n採購理當跟A承包下標，屆時採購發現了新天地AMD這神奇的公司，一樣八核心價格卻只要Intel 的2/3價格，沒有不買的理由<br />\n<br />\n不顧IT與使用單位的反對，找了B包商買了100台AMD八核心...<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n規格：<br />\nAMD 2700X<br />\nDDR4 16G * 4<br />\n1T NVMe SSD * 2<br />\nQuadro RTX6000<br />\n-------------------------------------------------------------<br />\nB包商也在內部做過驗證(口頭說有)<br />\n上週開始上線測試<br />\n<br />\n1. 驅動VDI穿透顯示卡會無法正常驅動，會變成内顯<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n2. Guest 在切換的時候，ad本機部屬讀取非常慢，login要30~40秒<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n3. 3D Render 比9900K慢非常多，CPU使用率拉不上去<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n4. 最致命的是 驅動一直Crash，就重開機<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">整體來說就是AMD對於hypervisor、VDI、RDM、IO passthru<br />\n還有一段路要走..不要硬來，會出事<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />...</span><br />\n-------------------------------------------------------------<br />\nB包商說AMD 是小眾客製機，沒辦法退貨<br />\n周旋了一周，還是硬把機器退回去了<br />\n接下來看包商跟採購怎麼把這個鍋處理掉了<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">這件事給我們一些啟示，AMD雖然好但不是完美的<br />\nIntel雖然貴，但還是有些地方非他不行，真的讓人恨倒牙癢癢</span><br />\n<br />\n※註1 VDI虛擬桌面是指在遠端把伺服器架設好後，client登入後<br />\n　會把user的專案、部屬、都拉進來、就跟本機操作一樣<br />\n　差別是VDI 可以分授權，不用每台電腦都部屬全套軟體<br />\n　需要用到哪一個授權就登入哪一組VDI<br />\n　然後再從專案管理軟體Check out需要用到的專案<br />\n　可以幫公司省下不少的專業軟體授權費<br />\n<br />\n文章來源：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/OCLAB/permalink/632118810568914\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgroups%2FOCLAB%2Fpermalink%2F632118810568914&d=1zr6t4yB9inWhfXylFPsaXocbXMCqCW%2BK0Nx6tfHLyc%3D&h=c5c9fd46\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/groups/OCLAB/permalink/632118810568914</a><br />\n<br />\nAMD 用家點睇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14d53150778015c397006cd6e4a11205e0f4e0d6","tid":1062769,"uid":195348,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T10:06:37.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">顯卡</span>"},{"pid":"8944644c41d7299fd3110557bfcb3f509d58e587","tid":1062769,"uid":58882,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T10:13:04.000Z","msg":"睇埋條 link 入面 回應先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1fe76460896e6637db73323ef2d3fd0f1f1d0f8","tid":1062769,"uid":37232,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T10:23:17.000Z","msg":"見到貼宮姐, 笑左<br />\n<br />\n有冇試下AMD FirePro 黎下有冇事?<br />\n<br />\nintel / n記不嬲一伙"},{"pid":"3cd883e72f68d346f6355612babc67d743f7792c","tid":1062769,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8944644c41d7299fd3110557bfcb3f509d58e587","tid":1062769,"uid":58882,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T10:13:04.000Z","msg":"睇埋條 link 入面 回應先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T10:35:16.000Z","msg":"hi 視覺敘事大師"},{"pid":"de09391c0b043139e07a2ae1d58118d6f5e2c49e","tid":1062769,"uid":114720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T05:55:57.000Z","msg":"好明顯係disp